# ThreadSanitizer suppressions.
#
# Trevor Brown's recordmanager (external/recordmanager) synchronizes with
# platform fences and volatile idioms from setbench's plaf.h that TSan cannot
# model, so it reports false-positive races inside the reclaimers (e.g.
# reclaimer_debra.h's epoch announce array). Suppress reports whose top frame
# is in the vendored library; our own headers under include/lockfree remain
# fully instrumented.
race:external/recordmanager
race:external/setbench-common
